9863.text: [9863] StaticText ' Need to make a sweeping change? Agent mode helps you do it quickly by analyzing code, proposing edits, running tests, and validating results across multiple files.'

9879.text: [9879] StaticText 'Plans the path, handles the work.'

9880.text: [9880] StaticText ' Agent mode reasons through the problem, coordinates next steps, and applies the changes—while keeping you in the driver’s seat.'

9887.text: [9887] StaticText ' From renaming variables to fixing errors, agent mode manages the tedious tasks that might otherwise break your flow.'

9899.text: [9899] StaticText ', OpenAI o1, and Google Gemini 2.0 Flash to crush coding tasks fast or go deep when it counts.'

9905.text: [9905] StaticText 'Drop an edit. Watch it spread'

9909.text: [9909] StaticText 'Next edit suggestions reveal the ripple effects of your changes across your project—helping you keep everything consistent.'

9928.text: [9928] StaticText 'Code review analyzes your work, uncovers hidden bugs, fixes mistakes, and more—before a human ever sees it.'
